data.description: Don't miss your chance at a 2.75% fixed rate assumable mortgage!!! Brand new to the market, this 1,264 soft home is everything you've been looking for! Conveniently tucked away inside a well-established neighborhood in Cookeville city limits, this home is situated just minutes from Capshaw Elementary. This home offers 2 traditional bedrooms and a bonus room which could easily be turned into a 3rd bedroom. With 2 full bathrooms, a one car attached garage, and a 24'x30' two car detached garage, this brick ranch style home offers something for everyone! Schedule your showing today!!
